''''Cendrillon'''' d yiwet n tmacahutt taqburt i d yura umeskar (auteur) a latini 'Elien' deg tidmi tis III seld tlalit n asar [[Wp/kab/Σisa|'''Σisa''']]. 'Elien' iḥka-d amezruy n yiwet n teqcict tamaṣrit, umi qqaren Rhodope', umi yuker Igider taṣebaṭ-is, u yeweḍa-s ugelid ferɛuni 'Psammétique', i g wehmen deg ṣebaḍ aki. Dɣa yahed i waken slid taqcict isɛan aṣebaḍ aki ur izeweğ ara.

Tamacahutt aki n 'Cendrillon' telḥa d acḥal n tidmi u deg acḥal n tmura akw d imenzaw (continents).  Tura akka llant azal n 500 ilqam (version) ines, akk mgaraden-t: si tmacahutt n 'Rhodope', ar tin n w-alqem n tmurt n [[Wp/kab/Cenwa|'''Cenwa''']] i y ttwarun deg tidmi tis IX, ar win n tmurt n [[Wp/kab/Arminya|'''Arminya''']] n 'Bo Than' , neɣ alqem n uṭalyani 'Basile' umi isemm-a Tamcict m'iɣiɣden (La Chatte des Cendres) deg 1634, neɣ asummur (Ballet)n 'Rudolf Noureev', i y-llan d tumgi taskilant (Mythe littéraire) i sqedcen, umi yawden aṭas n imeskar atraren am : 'Luc Plamondon', ameskar usaru azawan 'Cindy, la Cendrillon des temps modernes' id yefɣen deg 2002.


[[Image:CendrillonGustave Doré.jpg|right|300px|thumb|'''Cendrillon''' aken i tt-isumen [[Wp/kab/Gustave Doré|'''Gustave Doré''']]]]


Isem n 'Cendrillon' ikka-d seg awal '''Iɣed'''. Di tmacahutt n Cenwa, taqcict nni isem-is 'Ye-xian', i cuban ar w-awal almani "Aschen", i bɣan ad yini '''Iɣed''', dɣa am w-awl n teğlizit "ashes" i d-yusan seg iwen n w-azar. 

Tamcahutt n 'Cendrillon' wid i-s yefkan iman, u aran-tt tettwasen ar ugar n medden di yal tamurt, d imyura n tmucuha 'Charles Perrault' deg 1667 s w-alqem ines umi yefka isem 'Cendrillon ou la Petite pantoufle de verre', akk d win n w-atmaten Almaniyen [[Wp/kab/Grimm|'''Jacob d Wilhelm Grimm''']] deg 1812, umi fkka-n isem [[Wp/kab/Aschenputtel|'''Aschenputtel''']]. 

Amyaru d umedyaz azwaw [[Wp/kab/Essaid At Maamar|'''Essaid At Maamar''']], yerra-tt id daɣen ar tazwawt. Isemm-a-yas aken i yella w-azar n awal 'Cendrillon' M-iɣiɣden. Di tmacahutt agi, anaf akk isem-awen, akk di medqan n tmurt tazawt. Atan amek i tella tmacahutt agi, i d ittwaksen seg asmel n tasekla, [[Wp/kab/imyura.net|'''imyura.net''']]. 


== M-iɣiɣden ==

'''Tiririn n tmcahutt n watmaten Grimm:  “Aschenputtell“ '''

sɣur [[Essaid At Maamar|Essaid At Maamar]] 



M-iɣiɣden Assmi tuḍen massa Ufella, tameṭṭut umeṛkanti ameqqran  n lɛeṛc awaquṛ, akken kan twala iman-is tenteṛ, tetsawam-itt-id tmettant, tessawel i yiwet yelli-s tesɛa, tesɣam-itt-id ɣur-s ɣef yiri n wusu i deg tella teẓẓel, tenna-yas:

A yelli n tasa, ili-kem d taqcict yesɛan anamek, ayen n dir akk xḍuy-as! Yakuc ad yili yid-m yal ass, ma d nekk a kem-id-ttwaliɣ seg igenni, ad ttɛassaɣ fell-am.

Akken tessuli ameslay, bernent wallen-is, teẓẓel-as i tmettant deg irebbi-s, taɣawsa tewweḍ bab-is.

Taqcict tessefqad aẓekka n yemma-s yal ass, tettru fell-as war cceḥḥa, teqqim daɣen d tuḥdiqt tuɣ-as awal.

Mi d-tewweḍ tegrest yessa wedfel am tmeḥremt tacebḥant ɣef uẓekka n yemma-s, akken d-tezzi tefsut, iḍall-d kan yiṭij akka acemma ɣef tmurt, iderrez-as baba-s tameɣra n rcil, yewwi-d tameṭṭut terna tegla-yas-d s snat terbibin.

[[Image:Aschenputtel.jpg|right|300px|thumb|[[Aschenputtel|Aschenputtel neɣ Cendrillon]]]]

Tullas-nni d-tewwi yid-s cebḥen wudemawen-nsen-t mačči d kra, maca ulawen-nsent berrikit am tuggi taqbuṛt yuli wabbu si ddɣel d wayen icemten.

Ngum akk d-rrsen iḍarren-nsen-t deg axxam, rrzan-d yir ussan imcumen ɣef teqcict d-teğğa yemma-s d tagujilt.

Tenna yiwet deg-sent i tayeḍ tullas-nni zdat-s:

I uqeṛṛ-agi n teɣyult, yid-neɣ ar a tedder?

Tennay-as i nettat s udem-is: “ Win yebɣan ciccu yezlu beɛɛu, win yebɣan lesfenğ yefk nanna-s”, daɣ kemm a tuḥṛict ma yella-yam pappa “ aɣrum” deg ul, yessefk a t-id-ssisnen-t tfettusin-im, ihi ɣas kker ɣef yiman-iw, cemmeṛ i iɣallen-im!

Zeḍment fell-as di snat yid-sent, kksent-as s wesxenzeq akk icettiḍen imelḥanen d tarkasin tatrarin telsa, ḍeggṛent-as deg wemḍiq n lqecc-nni tacekkaṛt i uglim d icifaḍ i idaṛṛen-is

“ Sersent deg-s ayen sersen waɛbaben di Tmazɣa”.

Nnant-as: Wali, wali ay agejdur akka tettṛeqṛiq zdat-neɣ s waṛquqen ahin a tt-yeččen, treffed aɛenqiq-is deg igenni am yelli-s n ugellid s uburrez d nnefxa! Aha rfed tiqesṛit-im tura, zwir akka zdat-nneɣ ɣer texxamt n usewwi!

Ttadṣant fell-as, ssenɛatent-as anida d wacu yessefk a t-ttḍummu yal ass.

Tudert-is gar-asent tugar tin n yal taklit di tallit talemmast, teɛkef seg wefraḍ n leɣbaṛ deg udaynin, aḍummu n iḥuccan deg axxam d beṛṛa, aseyyeq, anejruḍ n uṣaɣuṛ, asired n iceṭṭiṭen, taruẓi n tregwa di tebḥirin, aḥuccu n weslen d wulmu terna tettagm-ed aman si tala d wahin d tahin...

Ayen akk yugaren adrar-agi n leqdic yuran di twenza-s, d ddemmaṛ n yir lehduṛ d weskeɛrer-nni sskeɛrirent fell-as terbibin n baba-s.

Yal ma ttreḍqent wallen-nsent fell-as, ɣas ma s tuddma, ibibbi d ɛeggu i d-tekcem s axxam, rennunt-as urfan, surugent kra ɣef tɣerɣert am irden d wayen nniḍen, ttgallant deg-s ar tefru iḥuccan fell-asen am akken yessifiy uɣerbal aclim neɣ ma tuder-as teḥdert n weɣrum deg imi.

Ula d tameddit mar a tesred, tefser tgeswaḥt yekkren ngum tanekra n wass si rrḍiḥ d nnṭiḥ war asteɛfu, ur tt-id-yetṣṣaḥ ara ad tsers iɣsan-is deg usu, ala.

Teggan ɣef tɣerɣert s iri n lkanun, d iɣallen-is i d tasumta.

Rnant-as llaqubat, sawalent-as M-iɣiɣden imi tt-tuli tebrek seg wabbu yakk d wammus n iɣiɣden.

 

Yiwen wass yekker baba-tsent ad yerzu ɣer walzuz ( agdaz, ssuq ) s uɛawdiw, yesteqsa tirbibin-is dacu ssarment ad sent-d-yeglu yes-s,

yiwet tessuter deg-s icettiḍen imaynuten igerrzen, tayeḍ d tiwiztin.

Yuɣal yenna-yas i kemm a M-iɣiɣden, yella kra ad am-d-awiɣ ?

M-iɣiɣden: Teẓriḍ a ba, afurek amezwaru a k-d-iqasmen deg webrid m´ar ad taliḍ ɣef teɛrurt uɛawdiw ma d-tuɣaleḍ s axxam, qeṛṛem-iy-id aqeclaw-is, glu-yid yes-s ttxil-k!

Argaz yuɣ-asent awal, yuɣ-ed icettiḍen imaynut igerrzen d twiztin yerna yeṭṭf-ed s lemɛamda abrid n teẓgi s axxam akken a s-d-qasmen ifurkan.

Amezwaru d-yemmuger yewwet-it-id s acelqiɛ, yeɣḍel-as ula d lemḍella yelsa i uqeṛṛuy-is, igzem-d seg-s aqeclaw, yewwi-t-id yid-s.

Mi d-yewweḍ s axxam yal ta yeffka-yas ayen tessuter deg-s, maca ḥala M-iɣiɣden i s-yennan tanemmirt-ik a baba.

Azekka-nni tessefqed s aẓekka n yemma-s am yal ass, tewwi yid-s aqeclaw-nni, teẓẓa-t ɣef uẓekka, tettru, tettru, tettru almi uɣalen imeṭṭawen-is ugaren taɛwint, yeswa yis-sen uqeclaw-nni.

Aqclaw-nni yegma yerna yeffɣ-ed deg-s yiwen useklu “ ttejṛa “ igerrzen.

M-iɣiɣden tuɣal trezzu kraḍ ( 3 ) n tikkal deg ass ɣef uẓekka n yemma-s, tettru, tettɛenni s ddaw useklu-nni.

Yal tikkelt tettwali yiwen wefṛux d acebḥan yettaded ger ifurkan-is.

Mi tɛenna deg-s kra, a s-t-id-ideggeṛ din, din war tuzya d tunḍa neɣ yejneɛ yefneɛ, ugur ur yelli.

 

Yewweḍ-d wass ideg agellid n at Mliyikečč  ira ad isseḥḍer tameɣra ideg a tt-id-uraren iḍebbalen, icennayen, tawsa d w´aẓ akin, ad yenced akk tullas n yal tamnaṭ akken ad yefren mmi-s tin a s-yeččaṛen tiṭ.

Akken d-yewweḍ isalli tirbibin n baba-s n M-iɣiɣden, uccagent ɣer lewqam war ma uḥtament.

Ssawḍent-as isalli ula i nettat m´akken d-as-sawlent, nnant-as:

Aha tura eğğ leqdic-nni, iyya-d mmceḍ-aɣ iqeṛṛa-nneɣ, wenneɛ-aɣ, gerrez-aɣ, ssfeḍ-aɣ daɣen tarkasin alamma ttiṛṛiqent akken yessefk, nennubget s tujjma deg lbeṛj  ugellid ilmend n tmeɣra ar yesker akken ad yaf mmi-s tin a yessenquqlen ul-is, ad tuɣal d tameṭṭut-is.

M-iɣiɣden teqdec-asent akk ayen uṛğant sseg-s, maca tettru daɣen, acku ira wul-is a teddu ɣer ccḍeḥ ula d nettat.

Tessuter di yambaba-s “ tameṭṭut n baba-s” ad as-tanef ad teddu d yessi-s.

Yambaba-s: Amek a yelli? Kemm a M-iɣiɣden yugaren sidna Yub ar a yeddun s wammus d tebrek-nni yakk i kem-yulin ɣer tmeɣra ugellid?

Ula d icettiḍen d tarkasin n manwala mačči tesɛiḍ-ten am kemm am tezziwin-im, ad aɣ-d-ternuḍ tura ccḍeḥ-im? Ah a lalla, ah a lalla!

Seg akken teggumma M-iɣiɣden a s-tebru i wawal, terreẓ-as aqeṛṛu i yambaba-s s uɛenni, tuɣal tesseɣli-d imeslayen-agi deg imi-s taggara, tenna-yas:

Atan surgeɣ-am iɣiɣden ɣer teqbuct n tɛedsin, ad am-fkeɣ snat tmirin (sswayeɛ), ma tessawḍeḍ tsefḍeḍ akk lğeṛṛa iɣiɣden, terriḍ yal aɛeqqa yettiṛṛiq amzun werğin yumis, ad medleɣ allen-iw, ad am-anfeɣ ad tedduḍ yid-sent.

Taqcict akken tesla i lehḍuṛ-nni, teffeɣ ɣer beṛṛa, terra ɣer deffir teḥnact, tessawel s igenni:

 

'''Ay aɛssas ur neččax, ay at wassa d yimiren.'''

'''Azent-iy-id yakk ifrax, ceyyeɛt-iy-id itbiren!'''

'''Yelwa s tqabubt s txenfuct,'''

'''ad yesfed iɣiɣden seg teqbuct!”'''

 

Tekcem ɣer teḥnact, tessa yiwet n tmeḥremt tazedgant ɣef tɣerɣert, tesmar-ed ɣur-s tiɛedsin-nni s iɣiɣden isebken

fell-asent, teslal kan taqbuct-nni s waman almi s-d-čuṛen

sin itbiren tawwurt, din, din ḍefren-ten-id akk yefṛax yellan s ddaw igenni mecḥen akk iɣiɣden-nni.

Itbiren rran akk tiɛedsin s wenɣab d uɣiwel ɣer teqbuct, ur tewwiḍ ara timirt ( ssaɛa ) tefra taluft, ssrafgen akk yefṛax, uɣalen s imeḍqan-nsen.

Yennecṛah wul n teqcict almi d ayen kan, tɣil ad teddu ɣer tmeɣra war uguren, tewwiy-as taqbuct-nni i yambaba-s.

Maca tameṭṭut tenna-yas: Ala a M-iɣiɣden, ur tesɛiḍ ara icettiḍen yerna ur tessineḍ ara ad tcedḥeḍ, ad ṛwun kan deg-m medden tadṣa!

Akken twala tserreḥ daɣen teqcict d imeṭṭi, tuɣal tenna-yas:

Lemmer ad seffḍeḍ tikkelt-agi iɣiɣden seg snat teqbucin n tɛedsin di yiwet n timirt, ad tzemreḍ ad tedduḍ.“ Tenna-yas i wul-is“. D awezɣi ad tefru taluft am ta.

“ Akken d-terwi yambaba-s snat teqbucin n tɛedsin deg iɣiɣden, teffeɣ daɣen teqcict ɣer deffir teḥnact, tessawel s igenni:

 

'''Ay aɛssas ur neččax, ay at wassa d yimiren.'''

'''Azent-iy-id yakk ifrax, ceyyeɛt-iy-id itbiren!'''

'''Yelwa s tqabubt s txenfuct,'''

'''ad yesfed iɣiɣden seg teqbuct!”'''

 

Tessa timeḥremt tazedgant ɣef tɣerɣert, tesmar ɣur-s tiɛedsin-nni ulin iɣiɣden, wwḍen-tt-id daɣen sin yetbiren d imezwura, drus kan almi d-ddan yefṛax akk di lejfaṛ-nsen am tikkelt tamezwarut, ur yewwiḍ ara wezgen n timirt taluft tefra, Faḍma teɛqel argaz-is, ifṛax bernen s anida d-kkan.

Ul n teqcict yennecṛaḥ yules, tɣil dayen tewweḍ asirem-is, ad teddu ɣer tmeɣra.

ɣas akken tessas-ed ayen yellan d awezɣi, ayen yugaren daɣen tiwin n uyefki n tsedda di tculliṭ n mmi-s, n waman i ɣef mnaqaṛen idurar neɣ tukksa n tmellalin ddaw tsekkurt ur tettfaq, maca tennay-as yambaba-s:  Ur yelli dacu ad am-d-yawi yakk wannect-a, ala ur tettedduḍ ara yid-neɣ, acku ur tesɛiḍ ara icettiḍen yelhan yerna ur tessineḍ ara yakk ad tcedḥeḍ, ur nestufa ara ad ṛwun deg-neɣ medden tadṣa di lğal-im.

Tezzi-yas-d i M-iɣiɣden s weɛrur, ulint nettat d yessi-s-nni yessalayen iman-nsent, yettawin iɛenqiqen-nsent deg igenni si zzux d lfux ɣer tcariṭ zzuɣṛen iɛawdiwen, ğğant-as-d aḍu ɣer deffir, tḥulfa s yiman-is tmeɣduṛt amzun iseffeṛ-as wewtul.

Akken d-tufa tegra-d kan iman-is deg axxam, tekker terza ɣef uẓekka n yemma-as, tebded s ddaw useklu, tettɛenni, tessutur deg-s, teqqaṛ-as: 

 

'''“ Huzz iman-ik, mmhihed ttxil-k ay aseklu,'''

'''akken igenni ideg tella yemma, s wuraɣ d lfetta ad id-yeglu!”'''

 

Tecḍeḥ d mmi-s ugellidIḍeggeṛ-as-d wefṛux-nni acebḥan tiqnedyaṛ yettwaṛuccen s wuṛaɣ d lfeṭṭa yernay-as-d tibacmaqin yettwaksun s leḥrir i idaṛṛen-is.

S uɣiwel i telsa M-iɣiɣden tunṭict-nni n at igenwan, teṭṭef abrid s tazla s axxam n tmeɣra, ula d yambaba-s d yessi-s ur tt-ɛqilent ara, ɣillent akk d yelli-s n kra ugellid n tmurt nniḍen.

Tugar Nuja Uteryel di ccbaḥa s tqenduṛt d tarkasin-nni d-telsa.

Timcumin-nni ulac akk anta i wumi yenna wul-is deg-sent, ahat d M-iɣiɣden tagi, ma yella kra n tin i tt-id-yemmektin imiren, tɣil attan teẓẓel ɣef yiri n lkanun ulin-tt ilefḍan neɣ tseffeḍ iɣiɣden i tɛedsin.

Akken ḍallent wallen n mmi-s ugellid fell-as, yebded wul-is kra n tegnitt, lemmer i sen-yehwa i izan a s-ččaṛen imi-s, tawwurt teldi, rrgagin icekkaben-is wergaz akken yessefk.

Yessekna aqeṛṛuy-is zdat-s almi d tikli ad yessuden idaṛṛen-is, yeẓẓel afus-is ɣuṛ-s, yessuter deg-s s tedṣa n wul d leḥdaqa ma yella yehwa-yas ad tecḍeḥ akk yid-s.

Seg imi i d-as-rsen i ccḍeḥ deg sin yid-sen, iḥulfa wergaz s yiman-is amzun yekcem igenni wis sa ( 7 ), ur yezmir ara yak a s-iserreḥ akken ad yecḍeḥ d tayeḍ akken yella ngum a tt-iwali m´akken inṭṭeg am ifeṭṭiwej si ta ɣer ta.

Ula mar a d-mmeɣ kra n yiwet seg sut tinzar yezgan ulint d asawen, a s-teẓẓel afus-is akken ad yecḍeḥ yid-s, yugi, yeqqaṛ-asent:

D tagi, d tagi kan ar a ceḍḥeɣ! “ S nnig lewqam d txessaṛt”.

Akken qqaṛsen idaṛṛen-nsen seg uzedwi d uhuzzu n tqesṛit, d tikli ad tekkfu tmeɣra, tekker ad tuɣal s axxam, ira ad yeddu yid-s a tt-iwanes deg webrid, acku ira daɣen ad izeṛ ansi-tt d win tt-ilan.

Tesɣaffel-it kan almi yezzi udem-is ɣer tama nniḍen, tekka tawwurt tessenser iman-is, teṭṭef abrid-is s tazla, terwel.

Yemdekwal-d kan, iger tamawt teffeɣ, ulac-itt dinna, yeḍfeṛ-itt si zdeffir.

Akken d tikli a tt-awḍen idaṛṛen-is, tuɣ-itt tegnitt tessaweḍ yakan ɣer zdat wexxam, iwala-tt m´akken tekcem deg iseqqif, tezger-it kan, tekcem tessedreg aqeṛṛuy-is deg yiwet texxamt n yetbiren.

ɣas ur yessegmeḍ ara s tmuɣli, ur iwala ara sani terra, maca icumm-itt ɣer din i tekcem, yurğa-tt dinna melmi ar a d-ffeɣ, almi i d-yejba baba-s n M-iɣiɣden yufa-d mmi-s n ugellid yettṛağu taqcict, yenna-yas: Ttnadiɣ yiwet n teqcict, ad tili tekcem ɣer texxamt –agi n yetbiren, teffer.

Argaz yekker iɣḍel-d igenni ɣef tmurt, yesgerjej yakk taxxamt-nni, yeɣḍel-itt-id, yesteqsa ul-is, yenna-yas: Tezmer ahat ad tili d M-iɣiɣden? Terreẓ akk texxamt, ulac dacu  ufan.

Uɣalen kecmen s axxam, ufan tuɣ yiwet n teftilt d tamecṭuḥt kan akka, ula d tafat-is tettak anzi ɣer tin ttwalin wid yezɛillimen,

M-iɣiɣden teẓẓel ɣef yiri n lkanun am tnamit, udem-is ɣumment-tt tbuxin.

A ziɣ teffeɣ si tewwurt n deffir n texxamt-nni, tewweḍ s temzizzelt ɣer ddaw useklu-nni i ɣer tettɛenni, tekkes icettiḍen yakk d tarkasin-nni telsa, tesres-iten s ufella uẓekka n yemma-s, yeddem-iten wefṛux-nni acebḥan, nettat terra-d ijerbuben-nni iqbuṛen i idisan-is, tuɣal s lemḥirat s amḍiq-is n tguni, teḍla tibuxin i wudem-is, teẓẓel am ulaxeṛt ɣef yiri n lkanun, terratt i lweɛd ucexxeṛ.

