baba-s, yambaba-s d yessi-s uɣen abrid ula d nutni s axxam ugellid, nettat teɛna aseklu-nni n tjujtin, tenna-yas:

 

'''“ Huzz iman-ik, mmhihed ttxil-k ay aseklu,'''

'''akken igenni ideg tella yemma, s wuraɣ d lfetta ad id-yeglu!”'''

 

Iḍeggeṛ-as-d wefṛux acebḥan taqenduṛt yifen tin n yiḍelli-nni s waṭas.

Irgazen akk yellan din m´akken tebded ɣef yimi n tewwurt n wexxam n tmeɣra amzun tewwet-iten lmeɣla, ffɣen-d iseqdiḍen n wulawen-nsen, ḥala agur n tziri i ɣef terna ad temyuṭṭaf yid-s afus deg ufus.

Mmi-s n ugellid yella yeṭṭef tiɣmaṛt, allen-is ceṭṭḥent akka d w´akka ansi ar a d-tejbu.

Din din yenṭeg fell-as, yeẓẓel ɣur-s afus-is, yedṣa-yas seg ul, yessuter deg-s akken ad teccḍeḥ yid-s.

Seg imiren ḥala yid-s i d-as-yers i zzwitt, rrwitt, ulac akk tayeḍ i ira ad yecḍeḥ.

Tin yecmumḥen yid-s si tidak-nni ur tettawi ara tɣerɣert si nnefxa, yini-yasent: D tagi kan, d tagi, ḥala yid-s ar a ceḍḥeɣ!!!

Akken d tikli ad tekkfu tmeɣra, tuɣal s axxam, mmi-s ugellid yeṭṭafaṛ-itt s lexmata, ira ad iẓer anida tezdeɣ.

Tessemneɛ idaṛṛen-is ɣer yiwet n tebḥirt d-yusan deffir wexxam, anida akken yella useklu n tfirsin-nni tiziḍanin am tamment.

Teckunteḍ am jebbirdu ɣef useklu-nni, teffer aqeṛṛu-is ger ifurkan.

Mmi-s n ugellid ur yeẓri anida tedda, igenni yerfed-itt, tiɣerɣert tessebleɛ-itt.

Yurğa almi d-iɛedda baba-s n teqcict, yenna-yas: “Taqcict-nni tabeṛṛanit n yiḍelli, ula d ass-a tenser-iyi, ad tili teɛluleq ɣef kra n ufurek n useklu-agi n ifires”.

Argaz yesteqsa iman-is: “ tezmer ad tili d M-iɣiɣden”?, yewwi-d tagelzimt, ijeggeḥ akk aseklu-nni, yerra-t amzun d iɛekkazen-nni i ɣef yettali ssenğaq, ufan aḍu iceṭṭeḥ, ma d taqcict tsumm-itt tɣerɣert.

Akken kecmen s axxam, tedṛa-yasen am yiḍelli-nni, anida d wamek tella M-iɣiɣden i tt-in-ufan.

Nettat tuḥṛict tejgugel ɣef yiwen ufurefk si tama, tenṭeg am tebkitt ɣer wayeḍ di tama nniḍen, tneggez ɣer tɣerɣert, terwel, teɛna daɣen Aseklu-nni n tjujtin, terra-yas i wefṛux acebḥan icettiḍen icebḥanen, telsa ijerbuben, tuɣal s amḍiq-is n tguni, anida tt-in-ufan teẓẓel.

Ass wis kraḍ n tmeɣra, akken uɣen abrid-nsen daɣen iɛeggalen n twacult s axxam n ugellid, teɛna ula d nettat aseklu n tjujtin d-yemɣin ɣef uẓekka n yemma-s, tenna-yas:

'''“ Huzz iman-ik, mmhihed ttxil-k ay aseklu,'''

''' akken igenni ideg tella yemma, s wuraɣ d lfetta ad id-yeglu!”'''

 

Iḍegger-as-d taqenduṛt yifen akk tiqnedyaṛ ssnen yemdanen, werğin tella yiwet am nettat yerna-yas-d tarkasin n wuṛaɣ.

Akken tewweḍ s axxam n tmeɣra yebded-asen umeslay i lɣaci-nni yellan din, wa iɛṛeq-as dacu ad yini, wayeḍ ɣas ur yekcim ara ɛemṛayen, maca ur yezmir ara ad yessali awal, amzun yeṭṭef-it buberrak, yal wa, yal ta dacu n uɛewwiq d-yemlal.

Mmi-s ugellid ḥala yid-s kan i yecḍeḥ daɣen ula d ass-nni, yeṭṭef deg awal-is, yeqqar-asent akk i sut tɛenqiqin-nni yulin deg igenni:

ɣas sersemt iman-nkent, nekk d tagi kan, d tagi, ḥala yid-s ar a ceḍḥeɣ!!!

Akken d-yewweḍ lawan ideg a teqqel s iɣiɣden yuran di twenza-s, ira wergaz a tt-yissiweḍ s axxam, a tt-iwanes deg webrid, maca nettat tessenser daɣen idaṛṛen-is s uɣiwel m´akken yezzi udem-is s anda nniḍen.

Ula d netta daɣen d uccen, yendi-yas ticeṛkett war ma tfaq.

Yendeh i sin yemɣiden-nsen, yennay-asen: mi tt-twalam kan tusa-d, nneɣlet tiquftin n llazuq ɣef tseddaṛin, ur tettut ara ula d iran!

ɣas akken tessufeɣ-d iman-is si tseddaṛin-nni ideg d-as-teḍra am tin d-izegren asif aɛebbas mar ad yeḥmel, maca tessegran deffir-s tarkast-is tazelmaṭ, yeckunteḍ deg-s llazuq, yeqleɛ-as-tt-id.

Mmi-s n ugellid yufa-d tarkast-nni tessegra deffir-s, yerfed-itt, yufa-tt d tameẓyant, d taleqqaqt yerna d uṛaɣ akken ma tella.

Azekka-nni yekkr-ed mmi-s ugellid, yuɣ lewhi n webrid-nni tettaṭaf M-iɣiɣden yal ma s-terwel, yewweḍ ɣer zadat wezrib yellan deffir n wexxam-nsen, yemlal-ed baba-s d amezwaru, yenna-yas:

Ḥala tin i wumi ad tezg tarkast-agi n wuṛaɣ a yuɣalen d tameṭṭut-iw. “ Nnecṛaḥen wulawen n terbibin n baba-s n M-iɣiɣden akken yessefk, acku ɣur-sent tiqejjiṛin gerrzen-t”.

Tameqqrant deg-sent tewwi tarkast-nni ɣer texxamt-is, tedda yid-s yemma-s, maca ur s-d-tezgi ara, ur tezmir ara ad tessekcem tifednan-is timeqqṛanin.

Teffka-yas yemma-s ajenwi, tenna-yas: Axx gzem tifednan-im! Mar ad tuɣaleḍ d tameṭṭut n mmi-s n ugellid, maɛɛac ad telḥuḍ ɣef udaṛ.

Taqcict tuɣ awal n yemma-s, tegzem tifednan-is, tessekcem adaṛ-is di tarkast, tessebleɛ teqṛeḥ, teffɣ-ed ɣer mmi-s n ugellid.

Yessuli-tt s ufella n teɛrurt uɛawdiw-is, yesɣam-itt zdat-s, yewwitt yid-s a tt-yer d tameṭṭut-is.

Yesɛada-ten uɛessas zdat n uẓekka n yemma-s n M-iɣiɣden, qqimen sin yetbiren ɣef tcebbubt n useklu-nni n tjujtin, akken wwḍen ɣer zdat-nsen, ccnan-asen-d tizlitt-agi:


'''“ Tarkast teččur d idammen, tamnayt-agi ur tettnehcam.'''

'''Ihi tislit iwulmen, d tin n-teğğam deg axxam“.'''

 

Mmi-s ugellid iḍal ɣer tarkast-nni, iwala ttfeggiḍen sseg-s idammen, yebren aɛawdiw-is, yerra-tt s axxam, yenna-yasen:

Ala, mačči  d tagi i d tislit i d-iwulmen, yessefk ad tqis weltma-s tarkast-agi!

Tekcem ɣer texxamt, tessekcem tifednan-is war uguren di tarkast, maca agerz-is yegguma ad yekcem.

Tefka-yas yemma-s ajenwi, tenna-yas: Axx ggzem agerz-im! Ma tuɣaleḍ d tameṭṭut n mmi-s ugellid, maɛɛac a telḥuḍ akk ɣef udaṛ.

Tuɣ awal n yemma-s, tessekcem adaṛ-is di tarkast s timdeḥḥest, tessebleɛ teqṛeḥ am weltma-s, teffeɣ-d ɣer mmi-s ugellid.

Yerfed-itt ɣef teɛrurt n uɛawdiw-is, yesɣam-itt zdat-s, yewwi-tt a tt-yer d tameṭṭut-is.

Akken wwḍen ɣer zadt useklu-nni n tjujtin, ccnan-asen-d daɣen yetbiren-nni tizlitt-agi:


'''“ Tarkast teččur d idammen, tamnayt-agi ur tettnehcam.'''

'''Ihi tislit iwulmen, d tin n-teğğam deg axxam“.'''

 

Yessaked wergaz s idaṛṛen n tmeṭṭut, iwala iqaciṛen icebḥanen d-telsa uɣalen akk d izeggaɣen seg idammen.

Yebren-as aqeṛṛu i uɛawdiw, yerra-tt s axxam, yannay-asen: Ula d tagi mačči d nettat i d tislit iwulmen, yella kra n teqcict nniḍen tesɛam deg axxam?

Baba-s n M-iɣiɣden: Ala, ḥala yiwet yelli-s n tmeṭṭut-iw tamezwarut yemmuten. D tamecṭuḥt, tecmet, terka yerna tečcuṛ akk d iɣiɣden, d awezɣi ad tili d tislit iwulmen.

Mmi-s ugellid: Ssufɣet-tt-id kan ɣer beṛṛa a tt-waliɣ!

Yambaba-s: Ala, M-iɣiɣden tumes aṭas.

Mmi-s ugellid: Nniɣ-awen aha ssufɣet-tt-id a tt-waliɣ!

Teffɣ-ed tmeṭṭut tebra I wallen-is, tessedreg akka acemma udem-is s ifassen-is, tekna zdat n mmi-s ugellid, netta yefka-yas tarkast-nni n wuṛaɣ.

Teqqim ɣef yiwen uqejmuṛ yersen deg wefrag zdat iseqqif, tessufeɣ-d adaṛ-is seg tqebqabin-nni n wesɣaṛ aquṛan telsa,

Tessekcem-itt deg tarkast-nni n wuṛaɣ, tusa-d fell-as s lqis.

Yewwi-tt mmi-s ugellid ɣef ayesAkken d-terfed s uqeṛṛu, yessaked-itt mmi-s ugellid s allen-is, yeɛqel-itt d nettat i d taqcict-nni i ɣef niqal yerhen temẓi-s lemmer ur tt-yufi ara.

Isuɣ si tmendit, yennay-asen: D tagi, d tagi i d tislit iwulmen!!!

Yambaba-s d yessi-s ur d-tegri ara ula d tiqit idammen deg udmawen-nsent, tekkfa fell-asent ddunnit.

Mmi-s ugellid yewwi-tt di tkeṛṛust, akken wwḍen ɣer tewwurt tameqqṛant n beṛṛa n lbeṛğ-nsen, ccnan-asen-d yetbiren tizlitt-agi:

Tarkast-a war idammen, tuklalem tizet a tt-teččem.

Tewwid-d tislit iwulmen, ansuf yis-m a tuhdiqt, kcem!

 

Ass-nni i tendeh tmeɣra n rrcil “ Zwağğ”, yeɣli-d igenni ɣef tmurt, iwaquṛen derrzen yid-s tameɣra, usan-d ula d lɣaci n leɛṛac nniḍen d tmura nniḍen, sa ( 7 ) n wussan d sa ( 7 ) n wuḍan yeqqnen di tnelli reddḥen imenduyar, cennun icennayen, iɛum walluy d uṣubbu.

Agellid s timmad-is yennecṛaḥ wul-is ahdum imi tuɣal d tameṭṭut n mmi-s, ula d yambaba-s d yessi-s yesres deg-sent ayen ur nelli, selkent ayen ur ččint ɣef ayen ssɛeddant fell-as.

M-iɣiɣden d mmi-s ugellid akken i uɣalen d imɣaren, ddren s tayri di talwit almi d tagara n tudert-nsen.

